---
title: Tex-Mex Pulled Pork Nachos with Mexican Cheese Blend, Pico de Gallo & Guacamole
description: Why, oh why, do we only eat nachos as an appetizer? Who wouldn’t want to eat nachos for lunch? Well, we sure do and we bet you do, too! In just 15 minutes—with no restaurant required—you too can enjoy this genius lunch idea. Crunchy corn tortilla chips are fully loaded with hearty Tex-Mex-style pulled pork, homemade pico de gallo, a Mexican cheese blend, rich guacamole, and a sprinkle of cilantro and fresh lime juice.
